{"tid":666591,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"感冒終於有藥醫！","createTime":"2018-05-16T04:00:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T06:17:37.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"530ed4df96f6f8fe104d3c13c68fa6272fb58c5b","tid":666591,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T04:00:18.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">我們想讓你知道的是</span></span><br />\n<br />\n普通感冒是由病毒引起，所謂感冒藥其實都是緩減症狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，令病人舒服一點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。不過，有科研人員表示，初步掌握了治療普通感冒的方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/95733\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F95733&d=duMjyfxHMcZJy4sLcEKbzIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=8a4778d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/95733</a></div>"},{"pid":"abc170228a209e050fa17a02e037af0d03eea767","tid":666591,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T04:00:32.000Z","msg":"普通感冒（common cold）這種常見的小毛病可大可小。它是最普通的傳染病，但也是最難觸摸的疾病之一。它很麻煩，流鼻水、頭病、周身乏力，除了好好休息，現代醫學對於引發感冒的微小病毒，基本上是無能為力。今天，科學家說，他們或許已初步掌握了治療普通感冒的方法。"},{"pid":"6ae0e433b431008d0d6659a52006cfb6dc9ada27","tid":666591,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T04:01:06.000Z","msg":"普通感冒主要由鼻病毒（rhinovirus）引起，以接種疫苗或抗病毒藥物去預防有一定困難，因為病毒有很多種類，而且迅速演化，導致抗藥性。英國的科學團隊就想到，要攻克感冒，不應由病毒入手，而是由其宿主&mdash;&mdash;人類入手。<br />\n<br />\n病毒入侵後，會利用人體細胞內一種稱為NMT的蛋白質去建構保護殼，並在宿主體內不斷自我複製。倫敦帝國學院（Imperial College London）的研究人員正研發一種抑制NMT的化合物IMP-1088，令病毒難以發展出抗藥性，並希望最終把IMP-1088製成可吸入的藥劑。在實驗室內，把這種抑制劑應用於人類肺部細胞上，只消幾分鐘就開始產生效果。<br />\n<br />\n研究人員Ed Tate教授表示，以針對宿主的手法去控制病毒雖然是較為激進的概念，但應該行得通。他相信，在患病初期吸入這種NMT抑制劑可以阻止病毒自我複製和擴散：「即使是去到中期（即病毒已經擴散），也有助緩減症狀，這對那些患哮喘的人士很有幫助，他們在感冒時會感到非常不適。」"},{"pid":"eabd61ad3bacb796743f502bb27756a9b610a788","tid":666591,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T04:02:56.000Z","msg":"有份撰寫是次研究報告的Roberto Solari教授強調，現在尚處於實驗初階，還未通過動物測試，距離製成人類可用的安全藥物，尚有很長的路。科研人員估計，新藥有望在兩年內在人類身上做測試。<br />\n<br />\n研究報告：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41557-018-0039-2.epdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41557-018-0039-2.epdf&d=duMjyfxHMcZJy4sLcEKbzIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=7ce0237b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41557-018-0039-2.epdf</a>"},{"pid":"2f2de415bd84fa2b73d08a8877a244ae87483aaa","tid":666591,"uid":77569,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T04:04:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a9e0e003ae62bc9ba8b62300d094585ab6d5c74f","tid":666591,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f2de415bd84fa2b73d08a8877a244ae87483aaa","tid":666591,"uid":77569,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T04:04:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T05:02:27.000Z","msg":"開post前search過個網唔似content farm喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/關鍵評論網\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%E9%97%9C%E9%8D%B5%E8%A9%95%E8%AB%96%E7%B6%B2&d=duMjyfxHMcZJy4sLcEKbzIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=b9e7f8f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/關鍵評論網</a>"},{"pid":"c736faed996e68873a33dc0da3aa658514ee08fc","tid":666591,"uid":77569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T05:39:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f344a41e6425f6a26e565b4706199dc87769545","tid":666591,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T05:41:08.000Z","msg":"中藥，完"},{"pid":"b806ffa8e0585211f1cd99734818adfe8999a8da","tid":666591,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c736faed996e68873a33dc0da3aa6